Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.16,0:20:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Please?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.91,0:20:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.46,0:20:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother Sù,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.46,0:20:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't expect you'd come visit me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.59,0:20:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Quick, bring food and wine!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.14,0:20:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Please?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.79,0:20:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.60,0:20:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Many thanks, Brother Sù, for gifting me such a fine steed!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.02,0:21:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I truly don't know how to repay you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.90,0:21:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,A precious sword belongs to a warrior,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.04,0:21:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,a precious horse belongs to a hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.90,0:21:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother, you're a tiger of the world, \NRed Hare is a dragon among horses.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.59,0:21:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,This horse could only belong to you, brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.39,0:21:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheers?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.00,0:21:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheers.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.47,0:21:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Time does flies. Brother Sù, what are you doing now?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.97,0:21:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I am {\i1}Tiger-General of the Gentlemen of the Household{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.05,0:21:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Look how far you've gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.36,0:21:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Virtuous brother, are you content?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.13,0:21:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, now I serve under Overseer Dīng.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.00,0:21:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Virtuous brother, I hardly see you anymore
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.61,0:21:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,but I do often see your esteemed father.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.10,0:22:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother, you must be drunk!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.30,0:22:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,My father has been dead for many years.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.32,0:22:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,How could you meet him, brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.44,0:22:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no, I am talking about...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.17,0:22:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Overseer Dīng!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.51,0:22:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Very witty, brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.97,0:22:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.35,0:22:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I am not saying this to flatter you,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.40,0:22:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,but with your talents...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.75,0:22:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,why are you wasting them under Overseer Dīng?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.35,0:22:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I don't have a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.03,0:22:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.57,0:23:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Light the torches!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.00,0:23:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Light the torches!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.04,0:23:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother, you possess the talent to\Nhold the sky and sail the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.86,0:23:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there anyone within the four seas\Nthat doesn't admire you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.34,0:23:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Achieving wealth and prestige for you is as easy as taking from a pocket.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.46,0:23:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you say...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.80,0:23:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,that you have no choice?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.97,0:23:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother, don't you know this story,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.00,0:23:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,that a good bird chooses a good tree to perch,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.88,0:23:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,a good minister chooses a worthy lord to serve.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.51,0:23:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Nowadays, there are more people and heroes\Nin the world that have extraordinary talent!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.62,0:23:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother, if you continue to follow Dīng Jiànyáng,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.85,0:24:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,how can you build a meritorious career?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.15,0:24:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's difficult to find a worthy lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.81,0:24:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Foolish brother, I've come here\N precisely for your future career.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.00,0:24:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother, who do you think is the hero of our era?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.05,0:24:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother, there is no harm in speaking your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.37,0:24:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,No harm?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.67,0:24:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no harm.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.40,0:24:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.89,0:24:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Having observed the vast realm, among all the\Nministers, I consider them all inferior to...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.04,0:24:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.05,0:24:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Dǒng Zhuó!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.96,0:24:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.00,0:24:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you laughing?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.79,0:24:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother, even a hero such as yourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.16,0:25:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,as soon he hears Dǒng Zhuó's name,\Nchanges the color of his face!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.54,0:25:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Dǒng Zhuó truly is a hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.88,0:25:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother, you really know how to joke!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.70,0:25:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But how can that traitor be a hero?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.68,0:25:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Dǒng Zhuó is tyrannical and eyes of usurpation.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.11,0:25:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,How could everyone within the court not know?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.11,0:25:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,But you-
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.06,0:25:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.45,0:25:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,you only know his image,\Nand not his heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.51,0:25:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You only know one aspect,\Nand not the second.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.73,0:25:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The Emperor is weak,\N unable to control the ministers.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.08,0:25:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,How could all the officials at court not know this?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.56,0:25:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The Prince of Chénliú is\Nintelligent, strong, and astute,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.37,0:25:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,apter than the Emperor a hundred fold.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.40,0:25:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Again, how could all the officials at court not know this?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.10,0:25:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,They all have these thoughts,\Nbut nobody says it out loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.26,0:25:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.38,0:25:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,They fear leaving a reputation of disloyalty
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.98,0:25:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,and being labeled as criminals,\Nexploiting the chaos to usurp the throne.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.97,0:26:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,A weak Son of Heaven is easy to fool,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.73,0:26:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,but a strong Son of Heaven is hard to fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.64,0:26:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The court officials are loyal on the outside,\Nbut deep down they think of their own benefit.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.79,0:26:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Who do you think truly serves\Nthe empire and nation's spirits?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.09,0:26:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Dǒng is not like them,\Nhe dares to say what others dare not.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.31,0:26:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,He speaks words others would not say out loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.72,0:26:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,He dares the risk of leaving a bad reputation.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.92,0:26:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,He bears the accusations of usurpation.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.61,0:26:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The heart of Lord Dǒng is pure,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.02,0:26:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,the actions of Lord Dǒng are righteous!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.70,0:26:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Though I 've never heard such words before,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.13,0:26:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,they don't seem unreasonable.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.91,0:26:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.44,0:26:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,to depose the Emperor\Nis the road to usurpation!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.22,0:26:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.14,0:26:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Since ancient times, only the virtuous were able to hold paramount authority.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.81,0:27:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Presently, the Prince and Emperor\Nare both sons of the late emperor.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.80,0:27:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,If he assists the Prince in taking the throne,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.45,0:27:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,how is that usurpation? This is my first point.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.06,0:27:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The second:
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.17,0:27:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,When the late emperor was still reigning,\Nhe favored the Prince of Chénliú,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.22,0:27:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,that he intended to have him succeed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.88,0:27:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It was Empress Hé and Hé Jìn who forced a change in heir, a terrible mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.77,0:27:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Dǒng will now depose the Emperor\Nand enthrone the Prince of Chénliú
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.94,0:27:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,in accordance with the late emperor's original will,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.48,0:27:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,restoring the throne to the Prince of Chénliú.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.68,0:27:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,How is that treacherous?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.97,0:27:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,My dear brother, hearing your words is like\nclouds parting to for the sun!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.14,0:27:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You have enlightened me!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.17,0:27:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother, there are 10,000 reasons why you shouldn't\Nhesitate and miss such an opportunity!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.15,0:28:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,If someone as insignificant as me under Lord Dǒng can become {\i1}Tiger-General of the Household,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.02,0:28:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,then you, with your great courage and talents,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.53,0:28:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,are sure to have a meteoric\Nrise under Lord Dǒng.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.98,0:28:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You would quickly climb up the ranks and be rewarded beyond what you could imagine.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.00,0:28:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to serve him.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.33,0:28:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.46,0:28:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no way to do so.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.66,0:28:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.04,0:28:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,please look.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.26,0:28:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,This is?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.93,0:28:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Dǒng has long admired your reputation.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.17,0:28:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,He intends to make a friend of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.82,0:28:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Dǒng ordered me to give you\Nthese gifts to pay his respects.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.39,0:28:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That precious horse, Red Hare,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.10,0:28:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,was Lord Dǒng's favorite mount.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.29,0:28:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Dǒng sends it as a special gift to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.15,0:29:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Dǒng
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.71,0:29:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,shows me such kindness.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.37,0:29:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Virtuous brother, Lord Dǒng has been thinking of your great name for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.68,0:29:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Dǒng has shown me so much favor,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.06,0:29:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,but I regret that I, Lǚ Bù,\Nhave done nothing in return,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.15,0:29:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no gift to offer when I meet him!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.21,0:29:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Virtuous brother, the merits you seek are here and it is as easy as turning your hand over.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.01,0:29:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Whom does Lord Dǒng want to eliminate?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.86,0:29:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You must know who.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.24,0:30:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I only fear...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.16,0:30:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You wouldn't be willing to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.06,0:30:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,My son, what's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.11,0:30:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,How could I, a real man, ever be your son?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.63,0:30:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Fèngxiān! Why are you saying this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.21,0:31:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Obtaining you, General, is like a seedling tasting sweet-dew in a drought!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.62,0:31:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.28,0:31:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Quickly, please rise.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.94,0:31:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.14,0:31:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Please sit.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.04,0:31:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I have wandered half my life. My only regret was not having met such a worthy lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.04,0:31:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord, if you would allow,\NI, Bù, would treat you as his own father.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.13,0:31:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Now Fèngxiān is by my side! Heaven has blessed me with such an outstanding hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.32,0:31:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,My son, please rise.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.38,0:31:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,My son, please rise.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.58,0:32:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Father, from now on, your son will follow you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.71,0:32:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Through water and fire, I will never give in!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.32,0:32:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I aid you to achieve this grand undertaking!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.36,0:32:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,With Fèngxiān with me,\NI can accomplish my ambitions!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.64,0:32:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Fèngxiān, my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.22,0:32:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.15,0:32:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I hereby name you {\i1}Chief Cavalry-Commander of the Gentlemen of the Household{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.80,0:32:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,with the noble rank of Marquis.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.70,0:32:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, father.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.20,0:32:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Present golden armor\Nand silk brocade robe.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.10,0:32:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow, your father will summon the officials to re-discuss deposing the Emperor.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.88,0:32:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Your son is willing to escort you, father!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.99,0:32:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I order you to bring 1,000 armed men\N to be your father's bodyguards.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.62,0:32:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I accept!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.00,0:32:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Gentlemen,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.55,0:32:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,the current emperor is ignorant,\Nunworthy to his forefathers.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.52,0:32:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I shall follow the examples of Yī Yǐn and Huò Guāng.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.46,0:33:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The emperor hereafter shall be \Nknown as {\i1}the Prince of Hóngnóng,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.50,0:33:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,the Prince of Chénliú will be the new sovereign.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.83,0:33:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Those who disobey will be...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.88,0:33:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,executed!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.28,0:33:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, the regime is still new,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.66,0:33:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,you were summoned to assist\Nthe Emperor to restore order!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.88,0:33:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yet you...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.14,0:33:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,have repeatedly called meetings to\Ndepose an imperial firstborn son!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.64,0:33:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you plan to rebel?!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.40,0:34:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The realm's affairs rely on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.98,0:34:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,If this is my command,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.77,0:34:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,who'd dare to oppose me?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.45,0:34:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The realm relies on the Emperor and the loyal ministers here!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.20,0:34:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.75,0:34:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,are merely just a traitor and a usurper!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.86,0:34:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Why should you matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.48,0:34:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Want to see if my sword is sharp enough, whelp?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.18,0:34:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Mine isn't dull either!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.77,0:34:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing's been settled yet! No need for strife!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.33,0:34:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Běnchū!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.48,0:34:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Běnchū...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.28,0:35:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,On the ninth month on the first day, we shall hold a ceremony of deposition and ascension at Jiādé Hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.28,0:35:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,All the civil and military officials must be present.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.50,0:35:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Dismissed!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.77,0:35:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yuán Shào!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.32,0:35:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yuán Shào!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.32,0:35:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What an useless official you are, unworthy of the empire's favor.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.23,0:36:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Dǒng Zhuó, you traitor!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.74,0:36:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Who told you to assassinate me?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.74,0:36:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You dare conspire against me?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.88,0:36:39.72,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(251.591,720)}Wǔ Fú\NStyled: Déyú
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.32,0:36:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(734.048,874.87)}You are not my monarch, I am not your subject.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.06,0:36:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(734.048,874.87)}What is there to 'conspire'?!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.18,0:36:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(734.048,874.87)}Your crimes upheave the very Heavens!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.08,0:36:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(734.048,874.87)}Everyone wants to see you dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.00,0:36:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(734.048,874.87)}I only regret not cutting you to \Npieces as to appease the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.92,0:37:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.20,0:37:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Bastard! Vile traitor!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.28,0:37:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You will go down in history as a byword of infamy for 10,000 years!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.70,0:37:33.86,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(296.196,645.196)\fade(255,0,255,0,450,20420,28200)}Emperor Shǎo of Hàn
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.60,0:37:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(715.318,912.273)}Emperor Xiàolíng left his subjects all too early.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.00,0:37:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(715.318,912.273)}The Emperor succeeded him as the heir and everyone within the four seas looked up at him.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.34,0:38:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(715.318,912.273)}However the Emperor is frivolous, inmajestic, and insolemn.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.64,0:38:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(715.318,912.273)}In the mourning of his predecessor, his father, he proved to be slow and indolent.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.20,0:38:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(715.318,912.273)}He is an embarrassment to the throne.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.88,0:38:07.98,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(263.414,511.949)\fade(255,0,255,0,500,1820,2220)}Empress Dowager Hé
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.12,0:38:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(715.318,912.273)}The Empress Dowager didn't teach her son\Nproperly as a mother should,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.34,0:38:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(715.318,912.273)}consequently the affairs of the realm are in chaos.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.78,0:38:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(715.318,912.273)}Empress Yǒnglè died suddenly,\Nwhich aroused public suspicion.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.04,0:38:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(715.318,912.273)}Isn't evident that the rules of the three essentials:\NHeaven, Earth, and Human, have been violated?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.84,0:38:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(715.318,912.273)}The Prince of Chénliú is dutiful, divinely virtuous,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.98,0:38:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(715.318,912.273)}and solemnly observes proper etiquette.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.02,0:38:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(715.318,912.273)}During the national mourning, he was sorrowful and has never said anything improper.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.85,0:38:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(715.318,912.273)}The entire realm has heard of his excellent behavior.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.72,0:38:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(715.318,912.273)}He is therefore suitable to rule the vast empire and unify it for the next 10,000 generations.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.37,0:38:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(715.318,912.273)}We hereby depose the Emperor,\Ndemoting him to the Prince of Hóngnóng.
